*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************
	EXPRESSIONS
*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************

if the sum of the question scores for a particular criterion > 0; then the criterion is scored as 1.

/AmountsTaken:			Substance taken in larger amount and for longer period than intended; Questions #1, #2, #3
/UnsuccessfulQuits:		Persistent desire or repeated unsuccessful attempts to quit; Questions #4, #22, # 24, #25
/TimeSpentObtaining:	Much time/activity to obtain, use, recover; Questions #5, #6, #7
/ReducedActivities:		Important social, occupational, or recreational activities given up or reduced; Questions #8, #9, #10, #11
/UseDespiteKnowledge:	Use continues despite knowledge of adverse consequences (e.g., failure to fulfill role obligation, use when physically hazardous); Question #19
/Tolerance:				Tolerance (marked increase in amount; marked decrease in effect); Questions #20, #21
/Withdrawal:			Characteristic withdrawal symptoms; substance taken to relieve withdrawal; Questions #12, #13, #14
/ClinicalSignificance:	Use causes clinically significant impairment or distress; Questions #15, #16

/SymptomCountScore:		sum of the individual criterion scores (excluding clinical significance) (Range: 0-7)
/DiagnosisFoodDependence: 1 = diagnosis met (symptomcount > 3 AND clinical significance = 1); 0 = otherwise


Note: question 17, 18, 23 are not scored but are used for primers for other questions

<expressions>
/AmountsTaken = if (values.q1 + values.q2 + values.q3 > 0) 1; else 0;
/UnsuccessfulQuits = if (values.q4 + values.q22 + values.q24 + values.q25 > 0) 1; else 0;
/TimeSpentObtaining = if (values.q5 + values.q6 + values.q7 > 0) 1; else 0;
/ReducedActivities = if (values.q8 + values.q9 + values.q10 + values.q11 > 0) 1; else 0;
/UseDespiteKnowledge = if (values.q19 > 0) 1; else 0;
/Tolerance = if (values.q20 + values.q21 > 0) 1; else 0;
/Withdrawal = if (values.q12 + values.q13 + values.q14 > 0) 1; else 0;
/ClinicalSignificance= if (values.q15 + values.q16) 1; else 0;

/SymptomCountScore = expressions.AmountsTaken + expressions.UnsuccessfulQuits + expressions.TimeSpentObtaining +
expressions.ReducedActivities + expressions.UseDespiteKnowledge + expressions.Tolerance + expressions.Withdrawal

/DiagnosisFoodDependence = if (expressions.SymptomCountScore > 3 && expressions.ClinicalSignificance > 0) 1; else 0;
</expressions>

*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************
	QUESTIONS
*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************
Note: by default all questions are required to be answered. To change
/required = false

<caption timeframe>
/ caption = "IN THE PAST 12 MONTHS:"
/ fontstyle = ("Arial", 3.0%, true, true, false, false, 5, 1)
</caption>


<radiobuttons q1>
/caption = "1. I find that when I start eating certain foods, I end up eating much more than planned"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q2>
/caption = "2. I find myself continuing to consume certain foods even though I am no longer hungry"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q3>
/caption = "3. I eat to the point where I feel physically ill"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q4>
/caption = "4. Not eating certain types of food or cutting down on certain types of food is something I worry about"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q5>
/caption = "5. I spend a lot of time feeling sluggish or fatigued from overeating"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q6>
/caption = "6. I find myself constantly eating certain foods throughout the day"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q7>
/caption = "7. I find that when certain foods are not available, I will go out of my way to obtain them. For example, I will drive to the store to purchase certain foods even though I have other options available to me at home."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q8>
/caption = "8. There have been times when I consumed certain foods so often or in such large quantities that I started to eat food instead of working, spending time with my family or friends, or engaging in other important activities or recreational activities I enjoy."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q9>
/caption = "9. There have been times when I consumed certain foods so often or in such large quantities that I spent time dealing with negative feelings from overeating instead of working, spending time with my family or friends, or engaging in other important activities or recreational activities I enjoy."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q10>
/caption = "10. There have been times when I avoided professional or social situations where certain foods were available, because I was afraid I would overeat."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q11>
/caption = "11. There have been times when I avoided professional or social situations because I was not able to consume certain foods there."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q12>
/caption = "12. I have had withdrawal symptoms such as agitation, anxiety, or other physical symptoms when I cut down or stopped eating certain foods. (Please do NOT include withdrawal symptoms caused by cutting down on caffeinated beverages such as soda pop, coffee, tea, energy drinks, etc.)"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q13>
/caption = "13. I have consumed certain foods to prevent feelings of anxiety, agitation, or other physical symptoms that were developing. 
(Please do NOT include consumption of caffeinated beverages such as soda pop, coffee, tea, energy drinks, etc.)"
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q14>
/caption = "14. I have found that I have elevated desire for or urges to consume certain foods when I cut down or stop eating them."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q15>
/caption = "15. My behavior with respect to food and eating causes significant distress."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q16>
/caption = "16. I experience significant problems in my ability to function effectively (daily routine, job/school, social activities, family activities, health difficulties) because of food and eating."
/ options = ("Never", "Once~na month", "2-4 times~na month", "2-3 times~na week", "4 or more times~na week~nor daily")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q17>
/caption = "17. My food consumption has caused significant psychological problems such as depression, anxiety, self-loathing, or guilt."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q18>
/caption = "18. My food consumption has caused significant physical problems or made a physical problem worse."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q19>
/caption = "19. I kept consuming the same types of food or the same amount of food even though I was having emotional and/or physical problems."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q20>
/caption = "20. Over time, I have found that I need to eat more and more to get the feeling I want, such as reduced negative emotions or increased pleasure."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q21>
/caption = "21. I have found that eating the same amount of food does not reduce my negative emotions or increase pleasurable feelings the way it used to."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q22>
/caption = "22. I want to cut down or stop eating certain kinds of food."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q23>
/caption = "23. I have tried to cut down or stop eating certain kinds of food."
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q24>
/caption = "24. I have been successful at cutting down or not eating these kinds of food"
/ options = ("No", "Yes")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1")
/required = true
/orientation = vertical
</radiobuttons>

<radiobuttons q25>
/caption = "25. How many times in the past year did you try to cut down or stop eating certain foods altogether?"
/ options = ("1 ~nor fewer times", "2 ~ntimes", "3 ~ntimes", "4 ~ntimes", "5 ~nor more times")
/ optionvalues = ("0", "1", "2", "3", "4")
/required = true
/orientation = horizontalequal
</radiobuttons>

*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************
	SURVEYPAGES
*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************

<surveypage YFAS1>
/caption ="This survey asks about your eating habits in the past year. "
/ subcaption = "People sometimes have difficulty controlling their intake of certain foods such as:

- Sweets like ice cream, chocolate, doughnuts, cookies, cake, candy, ice cream
- Starches like white bread, rolls, pasta, and rice
- Salty snacks like chips, pretzels, and crackers
- Fatty foods like steak, bacon, hamburgers, cheeseburgers, pizza, and French fries
- Sugary drinks like soda pop

When the following questions ask about “CERTAIN FOODS” please think of ANY food similar to those listed in the food group or ANY OTHER foods you have had a problem with in the past year

"
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q1]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS2>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q2, q3, q4]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS3>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q5, q6, q7]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS4>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q8, q9]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS5>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q10, q11]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS6>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q12, q13]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS7>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q14, q15]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS8>
/questions = [1 = timeframe, q16]
</surveypage>

<surveypage YFAS9>
/caption ="This survey asks about your eating habits in the past year. "
/ subcaption = "People sometimes have difficulty controlling their intake of certain foods such as:

- Sweets like ice cream, chocolate, doughnuts, cookies, cake, candy, ice cream
- Starches like white bread, rolls, pasta, and rice
- Salty snacks like chips, pretzels, and crackers
- Fatty foods like steak, bacon, hamburgers, cheeseburgers, pizza, and French fries
- Sugary drinks like soda pop

When the following questions ask about “CERTAIN FOODS” please think of ANY food similar to those listed in the food group or ANY OTHER foods you have had a problem with in the past year
"
